Package com.github.katjahahn.parser.sections.edata

Export parsing.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ExportAddressTable
    The export address table contains all relative virtual addresses in the order they are found in the export section.
    ExportDirectory
    Represents the directory table of the export section and provides access to the header values.
    ExportEntry
    Represents one entry of the export section.
    ExportNameEntry
    Creates an instance of an export entry with the name, ordinal and relative virtual address
    ExportNamePointerTable  
    ExportOrdinalTable  
    ExportSection
    Represents the export section of a PE file and provides access to lists of it's inner structures (export address table, ordinal table, name pointer table, data directory table) as well as access to a list of export entries fetched from these structures.
